channel.title: HELP QUICK! 517 error_game_js5connect!? Whole Server Nulled?
channel.description:
My server was running fine for a couple of hours. Everyone was having fun pking etc. Then all of a sudden, everyone disconnected. I saw nothing different on the server-side except everyone had logged out. Then and now when anyone tries to reconnect it says:
Loaded 52 custom sprites. error_game_js5connect
everytime.
I didn't change anything... I'm not sure what's going on... I reinstalled the latest version of JDK, restarted the server... checked my ports. Everythings fine. It even says: Received connection from useripaddresshere whenever someone tries to connect. But it won't let them get past Loading Updates 80% before saying Loaded 52 custom sprites. error_game_js5connect
Any help would be appreciated. :(
